records.addlTxt: Not to be in the City of Port Washington except for court. No contact with SEJ. No contact with address on Whitefish as listed in the complaint.  Defendant to avoid the victim's residence and/or any location temporarily occupied by the victim. The defendant avoid contacting the victim or causing any person other than a party's attorney or law enforcement officer to contact the victim. Contact includes: contact at victim's home, work, school, public places, in person, by phone, in writing, by electronic communication or device, or in any other manner.

1:12 PM Defendant Dexter Tyrone Love appeared by video from the Ozaukee County Jail, in custody.  Attorney Rachel Marie Boaz in court for Dexter Tyrone Love as a friend of the court.  Prosecuting attorney Benjamin Lindsay in court for the State of Wisconsin. Defendant qualifies for PD and has attorney Buckett on underlying case. Court advises of charges/penalties and finds probable cause. State recommends $8000 cash bail w/conditions. Counsel requests $500 cash bail. Defendant left video room prior to case completion.
Arraignment scheduled for November 15, 2022 at 10:00 am.
